desc_short	-----								After Reset RPG is an old-school hard sci-fi post-apocalyptic roleplaying game. An open world, developed with scientific accuracy and technical details. A nonlinear story with freedom of choice. A true hardcore CRPG game mechanics. Explore the wastes of the dead planet and forge your story!							
